## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="593d1-102"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> 是在 System.Speech 中实现语义技术的主要对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="593d1-102"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> is the primary object that implements the semantic technology in System.Speech.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="593d1-103">语义解释允许语法来定义使用规则识别引擎可以正确解释音频输入。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="593d1-103">Semantic interpretation allows grammars to define rules for use by a recognition engine to correctly interpret audio input.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="593d1-104">语义解释还可以识别引擎来组织其结果，以便它们可以更轻松地处理，而不是仅返回识别单词和单词的序列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="593d1-104">Semantic interpretation also enables recognition engines to organize their results so that they can be more easily processed, rather than returning only recognized words and sequences of words.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="593d1-105">例如，识别引擎输出"更改为红色背景"必须以进行分析和解释应用程序之前无法执行操作时。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="593d1-105">For example, the recognition engine output "Change background to red" would have to be parsed and interpreted by an application before it could be acted upon.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="593d1-106">一个<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar>对象可指定语义的转译，才能使处理更清晰易懂通过指定短语，有两个语义子结构，一个用于选择背景或前景 （由文本"后台"），和另一个用于选择（由文本"red"） 的颜色。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="593d1-106">A <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> object can specify a semantic interpretation to make processing clearer by specifying that the phrase has two semantic substructures, one for selecting background or foreground (represented by the text "background"), and the other for selecting color (represented by the text "red").</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="593d1-107">System.Speech 表示识别操作的树中的语义<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="593d1-107">System.Speech represents the semantics of a recognition operation in a tree of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> objects.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="593d1-108">每个<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>实例包括以下：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="593d1-108">Each <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> instance includes the following:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="593d1-109"><xref:System.Object>，可通过<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Value%2A>属性，用于键的实例<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="593d1-109">An <xref:System.Object>, accessed by means of the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Value%2A> property, used to key the instance of the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="593d1-110">语义分析的准确性度量值返回的<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Confidence%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="593d1-110">A measure of the accuracy of semantic parsing, returned by the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Confidence%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="593d1-111">名称/值对的集合 (<xref:System.Collections.Generic.KeyValuePair%602>) 的子对象，这两项也<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>实例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="593d1-111">A collection of name/value pairs (<xref:System.Collections.Generic.KeyValuePair%602>) of child objects, which are also <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> instances.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="593d1-112">子节点都可以通过访问<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>的实现<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602>使用的字符串查找键和一个<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>实例，如以下示例所示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="593d1-112">Child nodes are accessible through the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> implementation of <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> using a string lookup key and a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> instance, as in the following example.</span></span>  
  
    ```csharp  
    foreach (KeyValuePair<String, SemanticValue> child in semantics)   
    {  
      Utils.CreateSemanticsTreeNodes(semanticsNode.Nodes, child.Value, child.Key);  
    }  
