 <span data-ttu-id="593d1-113">基于 System.Speech 识别引擎提供的有效实例<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>对于从识别的所有输出，即使是对于短语与没有显式的语义结构。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="593d1-113">Recognition engines based on System.Speech provide valid instances of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> for all output from recognition, even for phrases with no explicit semantic structure.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="593d1-114"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>实例使用获取短语<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase.Semantics%2A>上的属性<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase>对象 (或多个对象从它继承，如<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognitionResult>)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="593d1-114">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> instance for a phrase is obtained using the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase.Semantics%2A> property on the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase> object (or objects that inherit from it, such as <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognitionResult>).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="593d1-115"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> 获取已识别的短语，而无需语义的结构的对象的特征是：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="593d1-115"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> objects obtained for recognized phrases without semantic structure are characterized by:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="593d1-116">缺少的子级 (<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Count%2A>为 0)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="593d1-116">The lack of children (<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Count%2A> is 0).</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="593d1-117"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Value%2A> 属性为 `null`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="593d1-117">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Value%2A> property is `null`.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="593d1-118">1.0 人工语义的置信度级别 (返回<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Confidence%2A>)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="593d1-118">An artificial semantic confidence level of 1.0 (returned by <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Confidence%2A>).</span></span>  
  
